textline.data: the system shall read data from pressure sensor
the system shall store the recorded pressure values in flash memory in fifo
the system will start alarm by turn off the led with alarm duration = "80 s
the system shall check if the pressure is lower than the predifend threshold ="20 bar "
thhe system shall store the pressure value in a flash memory
the system shall to inform the crew when the cabin has too high pressure
the system shall check the high pressure in the cabin
the system shall protect the crew from high pressure
